# Description

This is an internal project created to produce bundles of the so called resource manager.

This includes the following packets:

resource-manager

These packages doesn't have to be used in a project, they can be installed separately. They are however delivered through this project.

When checking out this project the first time, run:

```ncs-project update```

If there is a problem, please check the output from

```ncs-project update -v```

And also the man-pages for the ncs-project command.


## For Eclipse

If you are using eclipse, use the:

```
ncs-setup --eclipse-setup
```

In this directory to setup the classpaths correctly and create a Java
project.

Use File->New->Java Project, uncheck the "Use the default location"
and instead point to this directory.

For more information read the NCS Developer Guide.w
